               <msContents>
                  <summary>Image of Mary, መልክአ፡ ማርያም፡; Image of Jesus Christ, መልክአ፡  ኢየሱስ፡; Hymn to Mary, “All hosts of heaven glorify you,” ኵሎሙ፡ ሠራዊተ፡ ሰማያት፡ መንፈሳውያን፡; Hymn to Mary, “I Praise Thy Grace,” እሴብህ: ጸጋኪ:; Asmat Prayer against Wild Animals,  ጸሎት: በእንተ: መስተሃድር:</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="1r" to="17v" facs="005">Fols 1r–17v</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2891RepCh172">Malkǝʾa
                                                  Māryām</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <locus from="17v" to="33v" facs="022">Fols 17v–33v</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2839RepCh123">Malkǝʾa
                                                  ʾIyasus</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i3">
                        <locus from="34r" to="38v" facs="038">Fols 34r–38v</locus>
                        <title>Hymn to Mary, “All hosts of heaven glorify you,” <foreign xml:lang="gez">ኵሎሙ፡ ሠራዊተ፡ ሰማያት፡ መንፈሳውያን፡.</foreign>
                        </title>
                        <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                     </msItem>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i4">
                     <locus from="38v" to="41v" facs="043">Fols 38v–41v</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3064RepCh344">ʾƎsebbǝḥ ṣaggāki
                                                  ʾo-mǝlʾǝta ṣaggā</title>
                    <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i5">
                     <locus from="41v" to="41v" facs="046">Fols 41v–41v</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Asmat Prayer against Wild Animals, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ መስተሃድር፡</foreign>
                     </title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
